title: Indonesia social media user penetration 2017 to 2023
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Share of group, containing a total of 7 data points.
In general Share of group has rose over the Year.
Share of group is slightly increasing from 2017 to 2020, and lastly roughly constant from 2020 to 2023.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2017 and 2018_.
Maximum Share of group, about 37.0 was reported at Year 2023
The lowest Share of group, of value 28.0 was reported at Year 2017
